node.text: We love Deoz! Yawl saw me and him go at it on the 1st episode of BratLovesJudy. Cuz I really didn’t think we should have to leave our house for 10 days!??! We can call on him whenever for whatever and he shows up.  Thanx for everything Deoz.  None of the construction delays have been his fault.
